title: Catalonian independence 'a bad idea' for economy
description:
Catalan President Carles Puigdemont has said he will declare independence from Spain within days, and the constitutional crisis has unnerved the makets. Federico Santi is an analyst with Eurasia Group and speaks to Ian King.
